item.description:

[quote=“Bobby, post:24, topic:158160”][quote author=jme_009 link=topic=215576.msg1879882#msg1879882 date=1194936315]
Thanks all Just one more year until I can legally buy booze(in Quebec, which is a 10 minute drive) If anyone is wondering, my birthday present is being combined with my Christmas present, I’m getting an 80 gb ps3 and a few games.
